C2 Matching Algorithm Enhancement_New HA: Test Case 1:During the trade allocation all quotes or orders testing in the book before the auciotn has started must be allocated using allocaiotn trade tyoe or Regualr configure and then rest will trade as Hal allcotion.Auction response will be cancelled. 2PDPM 1 customer and 1 MM

Test Case 2:HALO with LINKAGE:Inbound Cboe Quote during HAL Auction CBOE becomes NBBO and Trades with update Cboe Quote NYSE and AMEX. PMM allocation will takes place before the HAL auction and then HAL allocation. 2PMM 2MM 2 customer
Test Case 3:HAL with LINKAGE::when both CBOE and Away Exchange are at the same price CBOE trades FIRST
Test Case 4:HAL with LINKAGE::when both CBOE and Away Exchange are at the same price CBOE trades FIRST Incomming order will trade with Auction response
Test Case 5:HAL with LINKAGE::when both CBOE and Away Exchange are at the same price CBOE trades FIRST Incomming order will trade with Auction response

Test Case 6:During the ongoing HAL the inbound orders with price WORSE than the NBBO on opposite side join CBOE book. When the BOTR worsens (CBOE becomes part of NBBO) and there is an update event (new Auction Response) then system verifies NBBO and trade allocation occurs up to the Quantity of the auctioned order. Verify that among ALL responses with identical prices the Customer order trades first up to FULL Quantity and then “Hall allocation stratergy” will applied for the remaining orders at the same price Hall allocation stratergy

Test Case 7:During the trade allocation all quotes or orders testing in the book before the auciotn has started must be allocated using allocaiotn trade tyoe or Regualr configure and then rest will trade as Hal allcotion.AON with customer will get allocation only in the end

Test Case 8:During the trade allocation all quotes or orders testing in the book before the auciotn has started must be allocated using allocaiotn trade tyoe or Regualr configure and then rest will trade as Hal allcotion.AON with customer will get allocation only in the end.40 allocation

Test Case 9:During the trade allocation all quotes or orders testing in the book before the auciotn has started must be allocated using allocaiotn trade tyoe or Regualr configure and then rest will trade as Hal allcotion.AON with customer will get allocation only in the end.40 allocation. Timeout will takes place and order will trade in CBOE as Regular

Test Case 10:During the trade allocation all quotes or orders testing in the book before the auciotn has started must be allocated using allocaiotn trade tyoe or Regualr configure and then rest will trade as Hal allcotion.AON with customer will get allocation only in the end.40 allocation

Test Case 11:HAL with LINKAGE:Inbound Cboe Quote during HAL Auction CBOE becomes worse and Trades with NYSE AMEX and CBOE. During trade allocation all response recivd after auction has started must be allocated using allocation trade type of Hal allocation

Test Case 12:HAL with LINKAGE::when Incomming order comes after the auction end normally CBOE NYSE trades Incomming order will trade with Auction response and AMEX will not get any quantity because BOTR cahnges and Rest of the order will be booked

Test Case 13:HAL with LINKAGE::when Incomming order comes after the auction end normally CBOE NYSE trades Incomming order will trade with Auction response and AMEX will not get any quantity because BOTR cahnges and Rest of the order will be booked
Test Case 14:HAL with LINKAGE::when both CBOE and Away Exchange are at the same price CBOE trades FIRST Incomming order will trade with Auction response
Test Case 15:Verify that during sweeping and link away process the system verifies first the market conditions and then the trdae follows the best price condition
Test Case 16:HAL with LINKAGE:Verify the during X timer outbound non quote like order does not start new HAL when the CBOE TOB is resting Quote like Order only
Test Case 17:Verify that if the timer ends normally while CBOE is still awaiting responses from the Away exchanges then any shipped quantity with no response is Booked immediately at CBOE
